5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Pinjarra Hills"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Pinjarra Hills? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Pinjarra Hills, Pullenvale, Bellbowrie and Kenmore. Our 5-star instructors help Pinjarra Hills students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Pinjarra Hills is an exclusive, tightly held outer-western acreage suburb positioned between the Moggill Road corridor and the Brisbane River. Driving in Pinjarra Hills is defined by its deep tranquility — the few residential roads that service the suburb are extraordinarily quiet, making it an idyllic location for a nervous learner's very first lessons in vehicle control."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"However, the suburb is directly bordered by Moggill Road — a major multi-lane arterial. This stark contrast provides our instructors with a perfect lesson structure: starting in complete, distraction-free isolation, and then stepping directly onto an arterial road for advanced merging, speed zone management, and direct routing to the Kenmore practical driving test centre."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Pinjarra Hills learners test at the Kenmore TMR Customer Service Centre. Free pickup from Pinjarra Hills, modern automatic vehicles, Afterpay available. Book today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-100 flex items-start gap-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-primary text-xl mt-0.5","children":"📍